---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Skyhooked on Comfort | Family-Owned HVAC in Phoenix Since 2010"
  description="Meet the family behind Skyhooked on Comfort. EPA-certified HVAC technicians serving the Phoenix Valley since 2010. Read our story and meet our team."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-charcoal py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-sky/20 text-sky text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 font-body">
        Family-Owned Since 2010
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-white text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight mb-6">
        Comfort done right, by people who actually answer the phone.
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-charcoal-50 text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Skyhooked on Comfort is a family-owned HVAC company serving the Phoenix Valley since 2010. We started small — one truck, Marcus Torres, and a stubborn belief that customers deserve a real diagnosis, an honest quote, and equipment sized correctly the first time. That belief is still the whole company.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-10">
        <a href="tel:4801234567" class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-sky hover:bg-sky-dark text-charcoal font-display font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors shadow-lg">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
          Call (480) 123-4567
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-charcoal font-display font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors">
          Request a Quote →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-charcoal text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-6">
            From one truck to the Phoenix Valley's most trusted HVAC team.
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-5 font-body text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Marcus Torres founded Skyhooked on Comfort in 2010 after years working for large HVAC contractors across the Phoenix Valley. The pattern was always the same: rush the diagnosis, oversize the equipment, push the most expensive option, and get out the door. Customers paid more, equipment was wrong for the home, and callbacks piled up.
            </p>
            <p>
              Marcus started Skyhooked on Comfort to do the opposite. Run a real Manual J load calculation. Recommend the system that actually fits the house. Pull every permit. Stand behind every install. Pay technicians well enough that they stay long enough to actually become great at the trade.
            </p>
            <p>
              Today, Skyhooked on Comfort runs multiple trucks across the Phoenix Valley and has served thousands of homes and businesses throughout Maricopa County. We're still family-owned, still answer our own phone, and still send the same technicians back to the same neighborhoods so you actually know who's at your door.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-charcoal-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-charcoal/10">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            {[
              { number: '2010', label: 'Year Founded' },
              { number: '15+', label: 'Years Serving Phoenix' },
              { number: '500+', label: 'Google Reviews' },
              { number: '4.9★', label: 'Average Rating' },
            ].map(stat => (
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="font-display font-extrabold text-3xl text-sky mb-1">{stat.number}</div>
                <div class="font-body text-neutral-600 text-sm">{stat.label}</div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-charcoal/10 space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-body text-sm text-neutral-700">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sky flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
              AZ ROC-312489 Licensed & Insured
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-body text-sm text-neutral-700">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sky flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
              EPA Section 608 Universal Certified
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-body text-sm text-neutral-700">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sky flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
              BBB Accredited, A+ Rating
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- What We Stand For -->
  <section class="bg-charcoal-50 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-charcoal text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-4">What we stand for.</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-neutral-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Five principles that haven't changed since Marcus started this company in 2010.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          {
            icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 7.5l3 4.5m0 0l3-4.5M12 12v5.25M15 12H9m6 3H9m12-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>`,
            title: 'Right-Sized, Not Oversized',
            body: 'Equipment sized to your home with a real Manual J calculation — not eyeballed off the old unit\'s nameplate. Oversized equipment short-cycles, fails early, and costs more to run. We never quote a system we haven\'t measured for.',
          },
          {
            icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>`,
            title: 'Honesty Over Upsell',
            body: 'We diagnose, explain, quote. If repair makes more sense than replacement, we\'ll say so — even if replacement would mean more revenue. Your trust is worth more than any single invoice.',
          },
          {
            icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25"/>`,
            title: 'Respect for Your Home',
            body: 'Boot covers go on at the door. Drop cloths protect your floors and furniture. Every job site is left cleaner than we found it. This isn\'t extra — it\'s the baseline.',
          },
          {
            icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.436 60.436 0 00-.491 6.347A48.627 48.627 0 0112 20.904a48.627 48.627 0 018.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 00-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.57 50.57 0 00-2.658-.813A59.905 59.905 0 0112 3.493a59.902 59.902 0 0110.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.697 50.697 0 0112 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 017.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 100-1.5.75.75 0 000 1.5zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0112 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 006.75 15.75v-1.5"/>`,
            title: 'Real Expertise',
            body: 'Every technician is EPA Section 608 certified. NATE certification is preferred and supported. We fund continuing education hours every year because the trade changes fast and our customers deserve technicians who keep up.',
          },
          {
            icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 011.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 00.475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 00-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 01-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.563.563 0 00-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 01-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 00-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.563.563 0 01.321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 00.475-.345L11.48 3.5z"/>`,
            title: 'Skin in the Game',
            body: 'If you\'re not satisfied, we make it right at no charge. No fine print, no manager calls, no runaround. We stand behind every job because our reputation in the Phoenix Valley is the only thing that matters.',
          },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-neutral-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sky/15 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sky" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true" set:html={item.icon}></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-charcoal text-lg mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- Credentials Grid -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-charcoal text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-4">Credentials & Affiliations</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-neutral-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">The certifications and licenses that back every job we do in the Phoenix Valley.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {[
          { label: 'AZ Contractor License', detail: 'AZ ROC-312489 — Active, fully bonded' },
          { label: 'EPA Section 608 Universal', detail: 'Required for all refrigerant handling — every tech certified' },
          { label: 'NATE Certified Technicians', detail: 'North American Technician Excellence — industry gold standard' },
          { label: 'BBB Accredited, A+ Rating', detail: 'Better Business Bureau — top rating, zero unresolved complaints' },
          { label: 'ACCA Member', detail: 'Air Conditioning Contractors of America — industry best practices' },
          { label: 'Background-Checked Technicians', detail: 'Every tech cleared before entering your home or business' },
          { label: 'Fully Insured & Bonded', detail: 'General liability + workers comp — certificates available on request' },
          { label: 'Drug-Tested Workforce', detail: 'Pre-employment and random testing — no exceptions' },
          { label: 'Multi-Brand Authorized Dealer', detail: 'Carrier, Trane, Lennox, Mitsubishi, Daikin, and more' },
        ].map(cred => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-charcoal-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-charcoal/10">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-sky/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sky" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-display font-bold text-charcoal text-sm mb-0.5">{cred.label}</div>
              <div class="font-body text-neutral-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">{cred.detail}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- Community Section -->
  <section class="bg-charcoal py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-white text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-6">The Phoenix Valley is home.</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 font-body text-charcoal-50 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Skyhooked on Comfort donates service calls every year to local schools, churches, and senior centers across the Valley. When a neighbor can't afford what they need, we try to help. If you know someone in that situation, tell us.
            </p>
            <p>
              We sponsor local youth sports and participate in community events throughout Phoenix, Scottsdale, Mesa, Tempe, and the East Valley. This is where Marcus grew up and where his kids are growing up — taking care of the community isn't separate from the business, it is the business.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          {[
            'Community service calls donated annually to schools and senior centers',
            'Youth sports sponsorship across the Phoenix Valley',
            'Same technicians sent to the same neighborhoods — you know who\'s at your door',
            'Phoenix-based dispatch — we\'re your neighbors, not a national franchise',
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
              <span class="font-body text-charcoal-50 text-sm">{item}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- Meet the Team Teaser -->
  <section class="bg-charcoal-50 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-charcoal text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-4">Meet the team.</h2>
      <p class="font-body text-neutral-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">Every technician who might show up at your door, with their credentials, background, and a bit about who they are.</p>
      <a href="/about/team" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-charcoal hover:bg-charcoal-light text-white font-display font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors">
        Meet the Full Team →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-charcoal text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-4">
        Ready to work with an HVAC team that actually picks up the phone?
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body text-neutral-600 text-lg mb-10">
        Call us, text us, or fill out the form. A real person responds every time.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="tel:4801234567" class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-sky hover:bg-sky-dark text-charcoal font-display font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors shadow-lg">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
          Call (480) 123-4567
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-charcoal hover:bg-charcoal-light text-white font-display font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors">
          Request a Quote →
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-sm font-body text-neutral-500">
        <a href="/about/team" class="hover:text-charcoal transition-colors">Meet the Team</a>
        <a href="/about/why-us" class="hover:text-charcoal transition-colors">Why Choose Us</a>
        <a href="/about/careers" class="hover:text-charcoal transition-colors">Join the Team</a>
        <a href="/reviews" class="hover:text-charcoal transition-colors">Customer Reviews</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
